-- Consumer spend on Blu-Ray to top $1 billion: News Corp
-- 
-- Mon Feb 4, 2008 5:13pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/02/04/us-newscorp-bluray-idUSN0422705220080204

 

 LOS ANGELES  (Reuters) - News Corp NWSa.N expects an "uptick" in 2008 from sales of higher-margin Blu-Ray DVDs, and predicted that sales of the next-generation digital format would top $1 billion in 2008, according to Chief Operating Officer Peter Chernin. 

 (Reporting by  Gina Keating ; Editing by  Gary Hill )